{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Drivers of the Apocalypse</strong> is a high-octane action-driving combat game set in a vast, treacherous wasteland. You step into the shoes of Artemis, a junior mercenary working for Thunder Strike Force. Your mission? Stop deadly convoys, defeat powerful bosses, and survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260240/extras/DoA_Steam_gif_2.gif?t=1733475802\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Art of Tactical Vehicle Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combat is all about strategy and precision\u2014steal weakened enemy vehicles, jump from car to car in mid-battle, and use each ride\u2019s strengths to your advantage. If your vehicle gets destroyed, don\u2019t worry. Simply leap to another and keep fighting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260240/extras/DoA_Steam_gif_4.gif?t=1733475802\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Battles on wheels Like No Other</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With its fast-paced vehicle-swapping mechanic, <i>Drivers of the Apocalypse</i> offers a chaotic mix of driving and combat. The game features a series of epic boss encounters, challenging you to make quick decisions and master your driving skills as you take on the toughest road warriors in the wasteland.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260240/extras/DoA_Steam_gif_1.gif?t=1733475802\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Vehicle Combat:</strong> Switch between enemy vehicles on the fly.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Epic Boss Battles:</strong> Take down huge convoys and powerful leaders.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Post-Apocalyptic World:</strong> Explore and conquer the wasteland, using cars as your ultimate weapon.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260240/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733475802","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260240/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733475802","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260240/ad244797847711a378d32182c977426e60d8064d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733475802","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260240/ad244797847711a378d32182c977426e60d8064d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733475802","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Drivers of the Apocalypse</strong> is a high-octane action-driving combat game set in a vast, treacherous wasteland. You step into the shoes of Artemis, a junior mercenary working for Thunder Strike Force. Your mission? Stop deadly convoys, defeat powerful bosses, and survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260240/extras/DoA_Steam_gif_2.gif?t=1733475802\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Art of Tactical Vehicle Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combat is all about strategy and precision\u2014steal weakened enemy vehicles, jump from car to car in mid-battle, and use each ride\u2019s strengths to your advantage. If your vehicle gets destroyed, don\u2019t worry. Simply leap to another and keep fighting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260240/extras/DoA_Steam_gif_4.gif?t=1733475802\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Battles on wheels Like No Other</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With its fast-paced vehicle-swapping mechan